summary:
With more than 20 years experience of working for production companies, TV and advertising agencies, with particular emphasis on organisational and creative solutions, I have learned how to overcome problems, come with solutions, always thinking ahead and aspiring for new knowledge while looking forward to new challenges. 

Shooting Films and Commercials are my biggest passion. I am happy to be part of this wonderful industry.
